{"id":111,"date":"2025-10-26T09:13:40","date_gmt":"2025-10-26T09:13:40","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/themes.hibootstrap.com\/limpid\/?page_id=111"},"modified":"2025-11-06T11:13:08","modified_gmt":"2025-11-06T11:13:08","slug":"quantiferon","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/themes.hibootstrap.com\/limpid\/quantiferon\/","title":{"rendered":"QuantiFERON"},"content":{"rendered":"\t\t<div data-elementor-type=\"wp-page\" data-elementor-id=\"111\" class=\"elementor elementor-111\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-881e16b e-con-full e-flex e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"881e16b\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-487bfef elementor-widget elementor-widget-limpid-inner-page-hero\" data-id=\"487bfef\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"limpid-inner-page-hero.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t        <!-- Inner Page Hero Area Start -->\n        <div class=\"inner-page-hero-area\">\n            <div class=\"inner-page-bg \">\n                <div class=\"container\">\n                    <div class=\"inner-page-content\">\n                                                    <h2>QuantiFERON<\/h2>\n                                                                            <ul>\n                                <li>\n                                    <a href=\"https:\/\/themes.hibootstrap.com\/limpid\/\">Home<\/a>\n                                <\/li>\n                                <li>\n                                    QuantiFERON                                <\/li>\n                            <\/ul>\n                                            <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n                <div class=\"all-shapes\">\n                                            <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/themes.hibootstrap.com\/limpid\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/inner-page-shape11.png\" class=\"inner-shape1\" alt=\"Shape\">\n                                                                <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/themes.hibootstrap.com\/limpid\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/inner-page-shape3.png\" class=\"inner-shape2\" alt=\"Shape\">\n                                    <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n        <!-- Inner Page Hero Area End -->\n        \t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-104684c e-con-full e-flex e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"104684c\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e4f6bb2 elementor-widget elementor-widget-limpid-quant\" data-id=\"e4f6bb2\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"limpid-quant.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t        <!-- Quant Area Start -->\n        <div class=\"quant-area\">\n            <div class=\"container\">\n                <div class=\"quant-widget\">\n                    <div class=\"row\">\n                        <div class=\"col-lg-7\">\n                            <div class=\"quant-content\">\n                                                                    <h3>QuantiFERON TB Gold Plus Blood Collection Guidelines<\/h3>\n                                                                                                    <p>Provide clear information about the QuantiFERON-TB Gold test, a blood test used to detect latent tuberculosis infection (LTBI).<\/p>\n                                                                                                    <h5>\n                                        <span>01<\/span>                                        Draw 2 mL of Blood directly into QFT Plus Blood Collection Tubes                                    <\/h5>\n                                                                                                    <ul>\n                                                                                    <li>As 1 mL tubes draw blood relatively slowly, keep the tube on the needle for 2-3 seconds once the tube appears to have completed filling<\/li>\n                                                                                    <li>The black mark on the side of the tubes indicates the validated range of 0.8 to 1.2 mL. If the level of blood in any tube is outside of the indicator mark, a new blood sample should be obtained.<\/li>\n                                                                                    <li>If a butterfly needle assembly is being used to collect blood, a purge plain red top tube should be used to ensure that the tubing is filled with blood prior to the QFT-Plus Blood Collection Tubes being used.<\/li>\n                                                                            <\/ul>\n                                                            <\/div>\n                        <\/div>\n                        <div class=\"col-lg-5\">\n                            <div class=\"quant-image\">\n                                                                    <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/themes.hibootstrap.com\/limpid\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/quant.webp\" alt=\"QuantiFERON TB Gold Plus Blood Collection Guidelines\">\n                                                            <\/div>\n                        <\/div>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                                                                        <h5>\n                                <span>02<\/span>                                Tube Shaking                            <\/h5>\n                                                                            <p>Immediately after filling the tubes, shake them ten (10) times just firmly enough to coat the inner surface. Overly vigorous shaking may cause gel disruption and aberrant results.<\/p>\n                                                                                                                        <h5>\n                                <span>03<\/span>                                Tube Transportation                            <\/h5>\n                                                                            <p>Immediately after filling the tubes, shake them ten (10) times just firmly enough to coat the inner surface. Overly vigorous shaking may cause gel disruption and aberrant results.<\/p>\n                                                                            <ul>\n                                                                    <li>As 1 mL tubes draw blood relatively slowly, keep the tube on the needle for 2-3 seconds once the tube appears to have completed filling<\/li>\n                                                                    <li>The black mark on the side of the tubes indicates the validated range of 0.8 to 1.2 mL. If the level of blood in any tube is outside of the indicator mark, a new blood sample should be obtained.<\/li>\n                                                            <\/ul>\n                                                            <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n        <!-- Quant Area End -->\n        \t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>QuantiFERON Home QuantiFERON QuantiFERON TB Gold Plus Blood Collection Guidelines Provide clear information about the QuantiFERON-TB Gold test, a blood test used to detect latent tuberculosis infection (LTBI). 01 Draw 2 mL of Blood directly into QFT Plus Blood Collection Tubes As 1 mL tubes draw blood relatively slowly, keep the tube on the needle <\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"elementor_header_footer","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-111","page","type-page","status-publish","hentry"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/themes.hibootstrap.com\/limpid\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/111","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/themes.hibootstrap.com\/limpid\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/themes.hibootstrap.com\/limpid\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/themes.hibootstrap.com\/limpid\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/themes.hibootstrap.com\/limpid\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=111"}],"version-history":[{"count":22,"href":"https:\/\/themes.hibootstrap.com\/limpid\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/111\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":1559,"href":"https:\/\/themes.hibootstrap.com\/limpid\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/111\/revisions\/1559"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/themes.hibootstrap.com\/limpid\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=111"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}